  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Physiotherapist (Home Based)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is expanding their team. They are looking for a registered <strong>Physiotherapist </strong>to conduct home based physical therapy sessions for clients.<br /></p><p><strong>Job responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct home based physical therapy sessions;</li><li>Oversee and monitor rehabilitative exercise programmes for individual clients;</li><li>Develop and implement appropriate programs to improve the overall wellbeing of the client;</li><li>To be able to support neuro related cases and geriatric type clients;</li><li>Provide advice and protocols in conducting rehabilitative exercise programmes;</li><li>Provide clinical advice on handling of clients with chronic illnesses;</li><li>Work with Exercise Specialist to execute programmes;</li><li>Maintain database/records of all clients to provide evidence-based exercise programme with accurate and appropriate documentation;</li><li>Ensure proper case notes for all clients;</li><li>Collate data from outcome measures and provide review and analysis of data;</li><li>Any other duty as assigned by Director of the team or Lead Physiotherapist.</li></ul><p>Work schedule: Tuesday to Saturday<br />Travel expense is covered.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Obtained Full or Restricted Registration and a valid practising License with the Singapore Allied Health Professional Council (AHPC);</li><li>Degree or Diploma from a recognised institution;</li><li>Preferably 2 or 3 years clinical experience;</li><li>Be a team player with excellent communication skills;</li><li>Able to work independently;</li><li>Willingness to learn;</li><li>Experience in geriatric and/or neuro cases.</li></ul><p>For clarifications, please contact Karyn Choo (EA Personnel Reg: R24120779) <a href=\"mailto:karyn@jobsjolt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">karyn@jobsjolt.com</a><br />Employment Agency: Jobs Jolt Private Limited</p><p>EA Licence No.: 24C2131</p><p><a href=\"http://www.jobsjolt.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.jobsjolt.com</a><br /><a href=\"http://www.remotejobsasia.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.remotejobsasia.com</a></p>",
